reviewText: Fun fun fun sequel to first Bhoothnath film.
It's rare that a sequel is as good as the original, but in this case, it was!
Love the premise of this movie and Amit Bachchan
Doesn't rate as well as the original movie.  Cute, but just watch the first again.
Excellent Movie and great Second to the First........ Great Meaning - Storyline and Awesome Acting!
